   "source": [
    "### Curve-Fit\n",
    "The built-in curve fitting function is `scipy.optimize -- curve_fit` \\\n",
    "The $r^2$ is defined as\n",
    "$$\n",
    "r^2 = 1 - \\frac{SS_{res}}{SS_{tot}}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "where sum of squared residue $SS_{res}$, and total variance $SS_{tot}$ is\n",
    "$$\n",
    "SS_{res} = \\sum_{i=1}^{n}{(y_{s_i} - y_{f_i})^2} \quad \\\\\n",
    "SS_{tot} = \\sum_{i=1}^{n}{(y_{s_i} - \\bar{y_s})^2}\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "c1340223",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
